<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<%- include('_head') %>

  <body>
    <div id="app">

      <%- include('_header') %>

        <div class="container">
          <ol class="breadcrumb">
            <li><a href="/">主页</a></li>
          </ol>

          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="bs-callout bs-callout-danger">
              <h4> 提问技巧 </h4>
              <p>
                1. 先去新大app查找。<br/> 2. 再去getting-started-with-javascript的<a href="https://github.com/xugy0926/getting-started-with-javascript/issues">issues</a>检索相关问题，找不到相关问题可以发起一个问题，老师会回答。<br/>                3. 最后还解决不了？或你的问题觉得很紧急？在微信群里问，问之前把问题整理好，尽量提供详细信息。<br/> 4. 如果在微信群不好意思问，还给你准备了一个幼儿园班。<br/>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="container">
            <div class="well well-x">
              <ul class="nav nav-pills" role="tablist">
                <li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="/words">心里话</a></li>
                <% for(var i = 0; i < homeworkInfoList.length; i++) { %>
                  <li role="presentation" class="active"><a href="<%= homeworkInfoList[i].url %>">第<%= i + 1 %>次作业 <span class="badge"><%= homeworkInfoList[i].count %></span></a></li>
                  <% } %>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">GIT & GITHUB</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <% for(var i = 0; i < gitTopicsList.length; i++) {%>
                  <li class="list-group-item">
                    <a href="<%= gitTopicsList[i].url %>">
                      <%= gitTopicsList[i].title %>
                    </a>
                  </li>
                  <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">PPT</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <% for(var i = 0; i < pptList.length; i++) {%>
                  <li class="list-group-item">
                    <a href="<%= pptList[i].url %>">
                      <%= pptList[i].title %>
                    </a>
                  </li>
                  <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h3 class="panel-title">课程的技术文档</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body">
                <% for(var i = 0; i < topicsList.length; i++) {%>
                  <li class="list-group-item">
                    <a href="<%= topicsList[i].url %>">
                      <%= topicsList[i].title %>
                    </a>
                  </li>
                  <% } %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <%- include('_slider') %>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <img class="avatar" src="https://ws1.sinaimg.cn/large/006tKfTcgy1fi7s7vo8y0j30hs0hsaay.jpg"></img>
    </div>
  </body>

</html>